When my coworkers brought me to Odalis, the hole-in-the-wall vibe definitely caught my attention. We went really late, like 1:00 AM on a Friday night and the lady at the bar is amazing! I love listening to her Spanish and she is super nice. The apple martini special hits the spot. I've only had the 1/4 chicken meal with salad and yucca and it was succulent. The chicken is seasoned nicely, the sauces provided are fantastic, and the food came out fresh and hot. If you're looking for cheap, good eats late at night, come to Odalis 😊
